As for appetizers, we LOVE their crab puffs - and i want some now as I'm typing.
Had the egg roll, and eh, it was just an eggroll.
I would definitely recommend New Asian Kitchen to anyone who likes fresh and tastey Chinese food.
I keep telling them they should open up a location in Desert Ridge - heck, we'd probably keep them in business all by ourselves!

